&lt;p&gt;In the era of Web3, owning your content means more than just writing it — it means &lt;em&gt;truly controlling where and how it lives&lt;/em&gt;. By combining the &lt;strong&gt;Blowfish theme&lt;/strong&gt; (a beautiful, modern Hugo theme) with &lt;strong&gt;Unstoppable Domains (UD)&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;IPFS&lt;/strong&gt;, you can create a fully decentralized, censorship-resistant blog that’s as easy to update as a traditional site — but lives forever on the blockchain.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://kokerzhou.github.io/ProjectConsent/posts/202511-blowfish-ud/feature.png"/></item></channel></rss>